OL,5, Small businesses and unions have hit   
OL,6, back at the Bank of England's chief    
OL,7, economist saying people need to accept 
OL,8, they are poorer otherwise prices will  
OL,9, keep soaring.                          
OL,11,FHuw Pill said a game of "pass the      
OL,12,Fparcel" of workers asking for wage     
OL,13,Frises and businesses passing on higher 
OL,14,Fcosts was fuelling inflation.          
OL,16,FHe added there was a "reluctance to    
OL,17,Faccept" households were worse off.     
OL,19,FBut the Federation of Small Businesses 
OL,20,Fsaid his comments were "out of touch". 
